\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-check-aurora-application-status\/#How_to_Check_Aurora_Application_Status\" title=\"How to Check Aurora Application Status\">How to Check Aurora Application Status<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-check-aurora-application-status\/#How_to_check_Aurora_College_Application_Status\" title=\"How to check Aurora College Application Status\">How to check Aurora College Application Status<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-check-aurora-application-status\/#How_to_accept_the_offer_and_pay_the_Admission_Deposit\" title=\"How to accept the offer and pay the Admission Deposit?\">How to accept the offer and pay the Admission Deposit?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/how-to-check-aurora-application-status\/#Related_Answers_About_Aurora_Application_Status\" title=\"Related Answers About Aurora Application Status\">Related Answers About Aurora Application Status<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 40px; text-align: center;\"><strong>The Aurora College Admission is out for all students who applied for admission in the 2024 academic year. Do well to check your application status on <a href=\"https:\/\/www.auroracollege.nt.ca\/future-students\/admissions\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.Aurora.nt<\/a><a href=\"http:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">.<\/a>ca to enable you know the required information needed to avoid forfeiting admission.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-check-aurora-application-status\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Check_Aurora_Application_Status\"><\/span><strong>How to Check Aurora Application Status<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To view the status of your application, including outstanding necessities, please kindly login in to the University online application system to view your admission application status.<\/p>\n<p>Click <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.auroracollege.nt.ca\/future-students\/admissions\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/strong> to view University\u2019s Admission Application Status<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-check-aurora-college-application-status\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_check_Aurora_College_Application_Status\"><\/span><strong>How to check Aurora College Application Status<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3 id=\"how-to-accept-the-offer-and-pay-the-admission-deposit\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_accept_the_offer_and_pay_the_Admission_Deposit\"><\/span><strong>How to accept the offer and pay the Admission Deposit?<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Using <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.auroracollege.nt.ca\/future-students\/admissions\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.Aurora.nt.ca<\/a><\/strong>. To accept your offer of admission and pay the affirmation deposit where relevant.<\/li>\n<li>click <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/aurora-college-tuition-fees\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><\/strong> to see fees directives for payment<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>The next step is to enroll online; an exact date will be issued to you by the university.<\/p>\n<p>Your account will help you track all things you need to know before and after being admitted.<\/p>\n<p><strong><em>And now you know how to check your application status by checking your student\u2019s account we hope this information was helpful kindly drop your comment in the comment box as we look toward your expectations.<\/em><\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>See also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<\/strong><a title=\"Aurora College Requirements\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/aurora-college-requirements\/\" rel=\"bookmark nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Aurora College Requirements<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<div class=\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\/10 dark:border-gray-900\/50 dark:bg-gray-800\">\n<div class=\"text-base gap-4 md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-3xl p-4 md:py-6 flex lg:px-0 m-auto\">\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\">\n<h2 id=\"related-answers-about-aurora-application-status\" class=\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Related_Answers_About_Aurora_Application_Status\"><\/span>Related Answers About Aurora Application Status<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"flex justify-between lg:block\">Here are some frequently asked questions (FAQs) about Aurora Application Status:<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"group w-full text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 border-b border-black\/10 dark:border-gray-900\/50 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-[#444654]\">\n<div class=\"text-base gap-4 md:gap-6 md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-xl xl:max-w-3xl p-4 md:py-6 flex lg:px-0 m-auto\">\n<div class=\"relative flex w-[calc(100%-50px)] flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3 lg:w-[calc(100%-115px)]\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-grow flex-col gap-3\">\n<div class=\"min-h-[20px] flex flex-col items-start gap-4 whitespace-pre-wrap break-words\">\n<div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\">\n<ol>\n<li>What is Aurora?<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li>Aurora is an online platform used by the University of Manitoba to manage student information, including application status.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>How do I check my application status on Aurora?<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li>You can log in to Aurora using your UMNetID and password to check your application status.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>What does my application status mean?<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li>Your application status will indicate whether your application is complete, under review, or a decision has been made.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>How long does it take for a decision to be made on my application?<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li>The length of time it takes to receive a decision on your application can vary, but you can contact the university&#8217;s admissions office for an estimated timeline.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Can I update my application after I&#8217;ve submitted it?<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li>In some cases, you may be able to update your application after you&#8217;ve submitted it. Contact the university&#8217;s admissions office for further information.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>What do I do if my application status hasn&#8217;t changed in a while?<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li>If your application status hasn&#8217;t changed in a while, you can contact the university&#8217;s admissions office to inquire about the status of your application.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ol start=\"7\">\n<li>What if I have trouble accessing Aurora?<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<ul>\n<li>If you have trouble accessing Aurora, contact the university&#8217;s IT Help Desk for assistance.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"How to Check Aurora Application Status, How to accept the Offer and pay for the Admission Deposit, Tuition&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":12974,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","fo